WEBVTT

00:00:30.168 --> 00:00:32.602
What are you thinking about?

00:00:35.206 --> 00:00:39.768
Why do you talk to Mom
when you're by yourself?

00:00:41.679 --> 00:00:44.477
Makes me feel better.

00:00:44.549 --> 00:00:47.985
Does she ever answer back?

00:00:51.589 --> 00:00:54.285
No.

00:00:56.127 --> 00:01:00.291
She never answers me either.

